short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A better Dark theme for SoundCloud

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An extension to get better Dark theme for SoundCloud in your favorite browser with coolest feature.

Features:
- Toggle theme (original light theme, SoundDark dark theme and auto theme followed the system setting)
- Dark theme :)

This extension is open source, released under MIT License. You can check our repository at GitHub (https://github.com/michioxd/sounddark)

Have any issue? Please feel free to share your concerns at https://github.com/michioxd/sounddark/issues.

This project is not affiliated with SoundCloud Global Limited & Co. KG.
